flowchart LR
    ACCEPT["Master Adapter 接受事务"]
    DECODE["地址译码/Target 选择"]
    RESERVE["预留 Master/Global/Target OSD"]
    REQ["请求网络\n路由/仲裁/Link"]
    TARGET["Target Adapter/Target 服务"]
    GRANT["Grant/中间响应"]
    WDATA["写数据网络"]
    FINAL["终态响应网络"]
    RETIRE["事务完成\n释放 OSD/Credit"]

    ACCEPT --> DECODE
    DECODE -.->|资源申请| RESERVE
    RESERVE -->|读请求或写命令| REQ
    REQ --> TARGET
    TARGET -.->|读终态响应| FINAL
    TARGET -.->|写 Grant| GRANT
    GRANT ==>|触发写数据| WDATA
    WDATA ==> TARGET
    TARGET -.->|写终态响应| FINAL
    FINAL -.-> RETIRE
    RETIRE -.->|Credit Return| RESERVE
    LEGEND["图例：实线=请求；粗线=写数据；虚线=响应或Credit"]
